# .gitignore — Austin Grading & Land Management site repo.
# Matched paths are NEVER tracked, pushed, or deployed. Comments must be
# on their own line (git has no inline comments).

# --- PRIVATE material (never leaves the machine) ---
# client/agency source assets, logos, photos:
/assets/
# internal retainer / strategy docs:
/retainer/

# --- BACKUPS (frozen rollback zips — never delete, never commit) ---
/website-deploys/

# --- Regenerable junk ---
node_modules/
.impeccable/

# --- Tooling that lives INSIDE the served site/ folder ---
# Kept locally, excluded so Cloudflare's site/ output serves ONLY website files.
/site/README-DEPLOY.md
/site/netlify.toml
/site/serve.ps1

# --- OS / editor clutter ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log
